{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad uſſehme to Otnêſſ\nKenafa Kahleba Brahta Dehls/\nkas jaunaks bija ne kâ wiꞥſch/\nun wiꞥſch dewe tam Akfu farwu\nMettu par Seewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikahs/ kad\nwiꞥna pee ta nahze/ tad tappe\nwiꞥna paſtubbinata no wiꞥnas\nTehwa weenu Tihrumu luhtt/\nun wiꞥna nolehze no ta Ehſeta/\ntad fazzija Kahlebs us tahs: Kas\nter tew?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta fazzija us wiꞥnu:\nDohd man weenu Swehtumu/\njo tu eſti man weenu Deenas\nWiddus Semmi dewis/ tad dohd\nman arridsan Uhdens Awochus/\ntad dewe wiꞥnai Kahlebs Awo-\nchus augſcha/ un Awochus letja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta * Kenitera Mohsus\nTehwotscha Behrni gahje no ta\n* Palmu- Pilsfahta us augſchu\nar Juhda Behrneem/ us Juhda\nTuſſneti/ kas Aradam prett\nDeenas-Widdu/ un nogahje un\ndsihwoja ſtarp teem Landim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Juhda zehlahs ar fa-\nwu Brahti Sihmeanu/ un tee ka-\nwe tohs Kananiterus/ kas Zewa-\ntâ dsihwoja/ un tsdeldeja tohs/\nun tee noſauze ta Pilsfahtu Wahr-\ndu Orma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Juhda uſſehme arridsan\nGazu/ ar wiꞥnas Rohbeschu/ un\nAſſlonu ar wiꞥna Rohbeschu/ un\nEkronu ar wiꞥna Rohbeschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS bija a-\nJuhdu/ ka wiꞥsch(tohs Ledſih-\nwotajus) no teem Kalneem is-\ndsinne/jo wiꞥsch ne warreja tohs/\nkas Eeletjâ dsihwoja/ isdsiht/ ta-\npehz ka teem Dſelsu Ratti btja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee nodeewe Kahleban\nEebronu/ itt ka Mohsus bij run-\nnajs/ un tas isdsinne no turrenes\nEenaka trihs Dehlus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Benjamina Behrn-\nne isdsinne tohs Jebusitexus/ ka-\nJerusalemê dsihwoja/ Bet tee Je-\nbustext dsihwoja ar Benjamina\nBehrneem Jerusalemê kohpa/lihd-\nskodeen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jahsepa Nams zehlah-\narridsan us Betelu/ un tas\nKUNGS bija ar wiꞥneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jahsepa Nams lik-\nBetelu iſluhkoht/ bet fcha Pils-\nfahta Wahrd8 btja pirnak Lus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Sarpi redſeja wee-\nnu Wihru no Pilsfahta ahra-\nnakam/ un fazzija us wiꞥnu:\nRahd jelle mums/ fur Pilsfahta-\nwarr ktuht/ tad darrisimi mehe-\nSchehlastibu pee tewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad wiꞥsch teem rahdi-\nja/ fur tee Pilsfahta warretu-\nktuht/ tad fitte tee to Pilsfahtu-\nar Sohbina Asmini/ bet to Wihr-\nru un twiffu wiꞥna Sainti lik-\ntee ar Meeru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nogahje tas Wihre-\nus to Getiteru Semuni/ un ustai-\ntija weenu Pilsfahtu/ un noſanz-\nwiꞥna Wahrdn Lus/ ichis tri-\nwiꞥna Wahrd8 lihds skodeen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Manaffus ne isdsinn-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
